   <body>
      <p>The <uicontrol>Form Load</uicontrol> event enables you to set values and attributes on a form after the form is generated. The logic is executed when you click <uicontrol>New</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>, or <uicontrol>View</uicontrol> the record, and the execution is completed when the form is generated.</p>
      <p>
         <uicontrol>Use Case# Set the value for a field based on user role</uicontrol>
      </p>
      <p>In the RFI form, if you want the company of the contractor to display automatically when a contractor is creating any record, then you can use the <uicontrol>Form Load</uicontrol> event to set the value for the appropriate field based on the user role.</p>
